channel.title: Rice Lake Bible Chapel
channel.description: Preach the word; be diligent in season, out of season; reprove, rebuke, exhort, with all longsuffering and doctrine. -1 Tim. 2:9
channel.itunes:summary: Rice Lake Bible Chapel is an autonomous fellowship of believers responsible directly to Jesus Christ who is the Head of the universal church. We are non-denominational in that we seek not to be divided from any other individual who has put their trust in the Lord Jesus Christ and seeks to honor Him.
channel.itunes:author: RLBC
